{
  "video_id": "d6Rgbw2ZzPY",
  "title": "Roxanne Meadows - \"Science, Values, & Social Change\"",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 280.0,
      "end_time": 2812.0,
      "text": "Roxanne Meadows attended Moore College of Art"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2946.0,
      "end_time": 5600.0,
      "text": "and graduated from Maryland Institute of Art."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6260.0,
      "end_time": 10206.0,
      "text": "For over 36 years she had her own company producing technical illustrations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10400.0,
      "end_time": 12760.0,
      "text": "architectural designs, and model making."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13586.0,
      "end_time": 16546.0,
      "text": "She and Jacque are co-founders of The Venus Project."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17170.0,
      "end_time": 19353.0,
      "text": "[Applause]"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 21540.0,
      "end_time": 24683.0,
      "text": "So, we are living in a time"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 24793.0,
      "end_time": 28491.0,
      "text": "when science and technology are racing forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 28855.0,
      "end_time": 31926.0,
      "text": "But our social systems are static."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32276.000000000004,
      "end_time": 35286.0,
      "text": "We do see people protesting in the streets, against"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35464.0,
      "end_time": 40730.0,
      "text": "the divide between the wealthy and the poor, racism, war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40590.0,
      "end_time": 43452.0,
      "text": "and sometimes they&#39;re able to overthrow"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43600.0,
      "end_time": 45618.0,
      "text": "the regimes that they&#39;re living under."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45895.0,
      "end_time": 51150.0,
      "text": "But only to put in another incompetent political government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51544.0,
      "end_time": 54251.0,
      "text": "that work within the monetary system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54400.0,
      "end_time": 57821.0,
      "text": "that cannot ultimately take care of the problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58449.0,
      "end_time": 62960.0,
      "text": "Jacque at a young age searched-… oh, excuse me!"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63830.0,
      "end_time": 67981.0,
      "text": "But, what The Venus Project has to offer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68418.0,
      "end_time": 71969.0,
      "text": "is a workable plan for social innovation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 72980.0,
      "end_time": 75476.0,
      "text": "using the methods of science and technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76800.0,
      "end_time": 81446.0,
      "text": "to enable everyone to enjoy the benefits of technology equally."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 82689.0,
      "end_time": 85538.0,
      "text": "Jacque at an early age searched for such a system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 85640.0,
      "end_time": 87427.0,
      "text": "but he was unable to find one."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 87661.0,
      "end_time": 89846.0,
      "text": "So he took on the job himself."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90141.0,
      "end_time": 94670.0,
      "text": "In order to accomplish this, he studied many different disciplines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94332.0,
      "end_time": 98399.0,
      "text": "understanding that science applies to everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 98676.0,
      "end_time": 102135.0,
      "text": "especially behavioral science, and I say that"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 102350.0,
      "end_time": 106744.0,
      "text": "because it’s the most neglected science in our culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 106898.0,
      "end_time": 111446.0,
      "text": "yet, the most important to understand the need for The Venus Project"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 111680.0,
      "end_time": 114240.0,
      "text": "and the direction of The Venus Project."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 115255.0,
      "end_time": 120609.0,
      "text": "I felt extremely lucky to have met Jacque when I was 27 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 120898.0,
      "end_time": 125414.0,
      "text": "I attended the lectures that he gave at his home in Coral Gables, Florida."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 126695.0,
      "end_time": 131846.0,
      "text": "And, the very first lecture that I went to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 132473.0,
      "end_time": 138110.0,
      "text": "Jacque in his “Fresconian” - his unique Fresconian manner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 138615.0,
      "end_time": 144596.0,
      "text": "proceeded to smash everything that I held dear and sacred."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 145950.0,
      "end_time": 148263.0,
      "text": "You understand that, huh? (laughs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 148695.0,
      "end_time": 152670.0,
      "text": "But what was different about him is that he replaced it."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 153830.0,
      "end_time": 156609.0,
      "text": "He didn’t just complain about society, but he replaced it"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 156935.0,
      "end_time": 159698.0,
      "text": "with a real viable alternative;"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 160104.0,
      "end_time": 165353.0,
      "text": "with a value system that appropriately accompanied it."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 166627.0,
      "end_time": 170860.0,
      "text": "So many people, when they first are introduced to The Venus Project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 170227.0,
      "end_time": 173858.0,
      "text": "they can’t understand why this isn’t implemented NOW."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 174295.0,
      "end_time": 177575.0,
      "text": "It seems so easy and it would help so many people."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 177975.0,
      "end_time": 182344.0,
      "text": "I usually say “Well, this is where we are in social evolution.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 183581.0,
      "end_time": 185149.0,
      "text": "But where is that exactly?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 186153.0,
      "end_time": 188529.0,
      "text": "The answer to that is quite complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 189224.0,
      "end_time": 193300.0,
      "text": "But the most relevant issue is that science"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 193747.0,
      "end_time": 195809.0,
      "text": "has very little relevance"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 196215.0,
      "end_time": 201520.0,
      "text": "to how we operate and organize society"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 201169.0,
      "end_time": 202880.0,
      "text": "and the way we live and think."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 204246.0,
      "end_time": 207483.0,
      "text": "Science presents us with the best tools we have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 208920.0,
      "end_time": 211409.0,
      "text": "to acquire a testable body of knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 211963.0,
      "end_time": 215174.0,
      "text": "It gives us a closer approximation to reality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 215630.0,
      "end_time": 217170.0,
      "text": "and shows us what works."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 218369.0,
      "end_time": 222258.0,
      "text": "When we become more self-critical"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 222473.0,
      "end_time": 226000.0,
      "text": "about our ideas, and test them in the real world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 226203.0,
      "end_time": 228920.0,
      "text": "we become more scientific,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 228461.0,
      "end_time": 232966.0,
      "text": "as opposed to wishful thinking and aspirations."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 233187.0,
      "end_time": 236610.0,
      "text": "The scientific method, just like science itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 236209.0,
      "end_time": 238566.0,
      "text": "is based on what was built before."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 239606.0,
      "end_time": 243458.0,
      "text": "So, observation, testing and experimentation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 243723.0,
      "end_time": 246720.0,
      "text": "took a long time to get to where we are today."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 247883.0,
      "end_time": 253249.0,
      "text": "And just very briefly, the scientific method is asking a question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 253673.0,
      "end_time": 257569.0,
      "text": "doing research in the field, trying to come up with a hypothesis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 257920.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261270.00000000003,
      "text": "and then doing controlled experimentation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 261175.0,
      "end_time": 263181.0,
      "text": "and reporting the results."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 264455.0,
      "end_time": 269298.0,
      "text": "Invention is serially developed, over a long period of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 270615.0,
      "end_time": 274443.0,
      "text": "For instance, a German engineer, Otto Lilienthal"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 274578.0,
      "end_time": 278381.0,
      "text": "was very interested, and admired, how birds fly."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 278861.0,
      "end_time": 284860.0,
      "text": "So, he stuck his arms in large wings and jumped off a hill."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 284763.0,
      "end_time": 286818.0,
      "text": "He wasn’t the first person to do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 286972.0,
      "end_time": 289667.0,
      "text": "but he was the first successful person to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 290541.0,
      "end_time": 294418.0,
      "text": "And he flew over 2,500 flights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 294763.0,
      "end_time": 297575.0,
      "text": "until the last one, that ended in his death."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 298190.0,
      "end_time": 299956.0,
      "text": "Others, after that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 300547.0,
      "end_time": 305450.0,
      "text": "experimented and added to the ability to fly, little by little."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 306763.0,
      "end_time": 310726.0,
      "text": "Some found out what didn’t work, which was just as important -"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 311353.0,
      "end_time": 312886.0,
      "text": "they put in the effort."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 314110.0,
      "end_time": 318726.0,
      "text": "We look at the early experimentation on videos, if you’ve seen them, of"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 319292.0,
      "end_time": 324369.0,
      "text": "people trying to fly with these contraptions that some people laugh at today."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 324683.0,
      "end_time": 328787.0,
      "text": "But they didn’t understand that that was the genuine exploration"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 328898.0,
      "end_time": 331440.0,
      "text": "to find out what worked and what didn’t."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 331673.0,
      "end_time": 333440.0,
      "text": "How else would they know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 334190.0,
      "end_time": 337803.0,
      "text": "The Wright brothers worked upon what was done before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 337913.0,
      "end_time": 339820.0,
      "text": "as I said is what science does."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 340160.0,
      "end_time": 344393.0,
      "text": "And they actually used a book from Otto Lilienthal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 344529.0,
      "end_time": 348953.0,
      "text": "which he wrote in 1889 about aerodynamics."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 349206.0,
      "end_time": 352535.0,
      "text": "He- … the Wright brothers based their aircraft"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 353460.0,
      "end_time": 354553.0,
      "text": "on his findings."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 355612.0,
      "end_time": 358473.0,
      "text": "So the Wright brothers weren’t the father of flight."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 359520.0,
      "end_time": 361107.0,
      "text": "They weren’t the father of anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 361286.0,
      "end_time": 364424.0,
      "text": "because so many people went before them and died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 364547.0,
      "end_time": 366793.0,
      "text": "so they could get off the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 368430.0,
      "end_time": 371772.0,
      "text": "It’s a long serial progression: invention."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 376633.0,
      "end_time": 378140.0,
      "text": "By the way ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 378412.0,
      "end_time": 382436.0,
      "text": "from the first small engine aircraft, in 1903,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 382830.0,
      "end_time": 386264.0,
      "text": "to today sending probes to Mars and beyond,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 386572.0,
      "end_time": 390276.0,
      "text": "all took place practically within Jacque’s lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 391236.0,
      "end_time": 394627.0,
      "text": "So, when you think about it, the last hundred years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 394867.0,
      "end_time": 397790.0,
      "text": "in the advancements in science and technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 398836.0,
      "end_time": 401796.0,
      "text": "were more than all the years that preceded it."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 402861.0,
      "end_time": 406700.0,
      "text": "Religious leaders tried to explain the world around them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 406886.0,
      "end_time": 410393.0,
      "text": "before a more comprehensive understanding of science"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 410870.0,
      "end_time": 415538.0,
      "text": "and its technology occurred, before a more comprehensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 415649.0,
      "end_time": 419410.0,
      "text": "understanding of the scientific method occurred as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 421181.0,
      "end_time": 427700.0,
      "text": "It was a primitive way to try and give meaning to living processes."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 429107.0,
      "end_time": 433230.0,
      "text": "It proclaimed a set of rules of right and wrong, and good and bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 433956.0,
      "end_time": 437489.0,
      "text": "that we are still inculcated with today."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 438683.0,
      "end_time": 444203.0,
      "text": "It had these rules or dogma to try and govern human conduct,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 444387.0,
      "end_time": 447766.0,
      "text": "without even understanding human need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 447883.0,
      "end_time": 451820.0,
      "text": "or the effects of environment on human behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 454529.0,
      "end_time": 459206.0,
      "text": "What they didn’t understand, they attributed to the gods."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 460412.0,
      "end_time": 465409.0,
      "text": "So, it really is a method of trying to control behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 465575.0,
      "end_time": 471126.0,
      "text": "based on fear, ignorance, and superstition."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 472836.0,
      "end_time": 476701.0,
      "text": "It is only through the methods of science that will enable us"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 476904.0,
      "end_time": 481181.0,
      "text": "to get out of poverty, hunger, and scarcity."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 482147.0,
      "end_time": 485452.0,
      "text": "Predictability comes from the use of science."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 486264.0,
      "end_time": 489840.0,
      "text": "For instance, scientists today can predict when the next"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 490430.0,
      "end_time": 493963.0,
      "text": "total solar eclipse of the sun will occur,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 494313.0,
      "end_time": 497132.0,
      "text": "where in all the world to stand to see it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 497427.0,
      "end_time": 501852.0,
      "text": "how long its duration will be, and exactly what time to view it."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 502732.0,
      "end_time": 507210.0,
      "text": "Sorry, but soothsayers, metaphysicians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 509335.0,
      "end_time": 513347.0,
      "text": "religious prophets, or philosophers"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 513581.0,
      "end_time": 518818.0,
      "text": "cannot come close to the accuracy that science gives us."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 519741.0,
      "end_time": 521784.0,
      "text": "No questions are out of bounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 522258.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524375.0,
      "text": "no matter how controversial they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 524492.0,
      "end_time": 528000.0,
      "text": "There are no sacred truths in science."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 528996.0,
      "end_time": 531101.0,
      "text": "Just like there are no bad words."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 531913.0,
      "end_time": 533938.0,
      "text": "You know, who are these people to tell us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 534430.0,
      "end_time": 536160.0,
      "text": "this is a good word, and this is a bad word?"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 536283.0,
      "end_time": 538455.0,
      "text": "This word you can use and this you can’t."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 538880.0,
      "end_time": 542984.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like a woman driving her car into a repair shop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 543452.0,
      "end_time": 547132.0,
      "text": "and the mechanic says “It’s the differential housing,”"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 547323.0,
      "end_time": 549483.0,
      "text": "or “the ball between the two wheels.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 549673.0,
      "end_time": 552800.0,
      "text": "And the woman gets (hah!) all embarrassed and says"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 552190.0,
      "end_time": 555975.0,
      "text": "“Don’t talk about that part of the car, put some panties on it!”"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 556920.0,
      "end_time": 557495.0,
      "text": "[Laughter]"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 557606.0,
      "end_time": 562800.0,
      "text": "For every concept that … we cannot discuss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 562289.0,
      "end_time": 564806.0,
      "text": "or every word we cannot utter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 565390.0,
      "end_time": 568492.0,
      "text": "determines just how backwards we remain."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 569409.0,
      "end_time": 572486.0,
      "text": "Without scientific scrutiny and critical thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 572781.0,
      "end_time": 574792.0,
      "text": "we would have a world of suckers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 574978.0,
      "end_time": 577949.0,
      "text": "pacified by the dominant values of the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 578227.0,
      "end_time": 580603.0,
      "text": "to keep things as they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 581446.0,
      "end_time": 582966.0,
      "text": "“Clean coal.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 583323.0,
      "end_time": 585458.0,
      "text": "“Global warming is a hoax.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 586360.0,
      "end_time": 588189.0,
      "text": "\"Smart\" weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 589298.0,
      "end_time": 592541.0,
      "text": "“There’ll always be wars and rumors of wars.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 593760.0,
      "end_time": 594596.0,
      "text": "“We all have free will.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 595169.0,
      "end_time": 597830.0,
      "text": "“Can’t change human nature.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 598120.0,
      "end_time": 600246.0,
      "text": "And the list of misconceptions"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 600363.0,
      "end_time": 604860.0,
      "text": "that help perpetuate old ways of thinking prevail."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 605353.0,
      "end_time": 608203.0,
      "text": "We don’t put the same critical thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 608338.0,
      "end_time": 611858.0,
      "text": "in examining our social system and our values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 612980.0,
      "end_time": 614540.0,
      "text": "as we do say even making a product."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 615618.0,
      "end_time": 618701.0,
      "text": "But this isn’t to cast blame on the individual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 618990.0,
      "end_time": 623667.0,
      "text": "because we can only think with the tools that we are given."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 623993.0,
      "end_time": 626141.0,
      "text": "We can’t exceed them."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 627846.0,
      "end_time": 630147.0,
      "text": "What we have to think with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 630270.0,
      "end_time": 634603.0,
      "text": "does not come from the inside out, but we totally"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 634800.0,
      "end_time": 637132.0,
      "text": "reflect our surroundings."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 637870.0,
      "end_time": 640246.0,
      "text": "If we could critically view"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 641138.0,
      "end_time": 645981.0,
      "text": "our movies, TV, Internet, books, magazines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 646221.0,
      "end_time": 649800.0,
      "text": "and what they pass off on us as entertainment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 650360.0,
      "end_time": 651944.0,
      "text": "we could easily see"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 652550.0,
      "end_time": 655569.0,
      "text": "that what they’re trying to teach our children and ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 656264.0,
      "end_time": 660430.0,
      "text": "is arrogance, cruelty, racism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 660332.0,
      "end_time": 663300.0,
      "text": "bigotry, violence, war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 663630.0,
      "end_time": 668867.0,
      "text": "chauvinism, murder, and endless commercialism."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 671300.0,
      "end_time": 676120.0,
      "text": "And they sure as hell are succeeding, without any concern whatsoever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 676153.0,
      "end_time": 678393.0,
      "text": "other than if it makes a profit."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 679883.0,
      "end_time": 683830.0,
      "text": "Science enables us to electrify our homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 683200.0,
      "end_time": 685163.0,
      "text": "travel from place to place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 685821.0,
      "end_time": 688190.0,
      "text": "talk to anybody, anywhere within the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 688313.0,
      "end_time": 690861.0,
      "text": "and even see them at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 692363.0,
      "end_time": 697260.0,
      "text": "It even gives us the gift of life itself through the accomplishments of medicine."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 697969.0,
      "end_time": 703538.0,
      "text": "Yet, it’s also a scapegoat for the plethora of problems that we have today."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 704504.0,
      "end_time": 706510.0,
      "text": "Because, it is ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 707532.0,
      "end_time": 712436.0,
      "text": "misused and abused by people who are conditioned in a sick"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 712720.0,
      "end_time": 714289.0,
      "text": "and primitive culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 716670.0,
      "end_time": 719931.0,
      "text": "where half the scientists in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 720480.0,
      "end_time": 723680.0,
      "text": "work for the military, at least part time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 723944.0,
      "end_time": 727617.0,
      "text": "and many others work for industries that pollute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 727864.0,
      "end_time": 730726.0,
      "text": "poison, and destroy the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 731310.0,
      "end_time": 733464.0,
      "text": "These are not scientists."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 733895.0,
      "end_time": 739680.0,
      "text": "These are prostitutes, or obedient opportunists."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 740603.0,
      "end_time": 743593.0,
      "text": "[Applause]"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 750572.0,
      "end_time": 755433.0,
      "text": "Things are set up where very few of us understand science and technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 755981.0,
      "end_time": 761144.0,
      "text": "Yet, our future depends on the progression of relevant information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 761280.0,
      "end_time": 762880.0,
      "text": "and how we apply it."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 763273.0,
      "end_time": 766295.0,
      "text": "The less knowledge we have of the real world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 767286.0,
      "end_time": 770891.0,
      "text": "the more pseudoscience and superstition and fear"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 771150.0,
      "end_time": 772872.0,
      "text": "creep in to fill the void."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 773550.0,
      "end_time": 776240.0,
      "text": "And we become easy prey"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 776230.0,
      "end_time": 778467.0,
      "text": "for bigotry, prejudice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 778775.0,
      "end_time": 781840.0,
      "text": "fanaticism, and misinformation."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 782516.0,
      "end_time": 787839.0,
      "text": "This is a volatile mix, for a devastating future."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 788276.0,
      "end_time": 791673.0,
      "text": "Because technology is excelling exponentially."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 792806.0,
      "end_time": 795156.0,
      "text": "Who is this ignorance serving anyway?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 796123.0,
      "end_time": 799520.0,
      "text": "Today, those in positions of advantage"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 800430.0,
      "end_time": 804110.0,
      "text": "seek to perpetuate the system that put them there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 804283.0,
      "end_time": 806295.0,
      "text": "often at any cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 807840.0,
      "end_time": 811501.0,
      "text": "And laws are written by large corporations"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 811655.0,
      "end_time": 813624.0,
      "text": "to benefit themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 814360.0,
      "end_time": 817563.0,
      "text": "And the military is there to protect them both."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 819193.0,
      "end_time": 821925.0,
      "text": "What would happen in a world without law and order?"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 822843.0,
      "end_time": 825396.0,
      "text": "There would be chaos, there’d be murder."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 825649.0,
      "end_time": 828996.0,
      "text": "People would be killing each other and stealing from each other -"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 830600.0,
      "end_time": 831555.0,
      "text": "just like it is today!"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 833846.0,
      "end_time": 837335.0,
      "text": "So, something’s needed, but it’s not law and order."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 837612.0,
      "end_time": 840762.0,
      "text": "Instead, it’s environmental conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 841580.0,
      "end_time": 845864.0,
      "text": "that don’t generate the need for human hostility."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 847550.0,
      "end_time": 852920.0,
      "text": "Science applied to the social system means that we have to generate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 852393.0,
      "end_time": 855790.0,
      "text": "we have to organize, and design an environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 856553.0,
      "end_time": 861636.0,
      "text": "that surpasses the need for poverty, hunger, war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 861766.0,
      "end_time": 863649.0,
      "text": "and aberrant behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 864572.0,
      "end_time": 866141.0,
      "text": "As a way out of our dilemma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 866270.0,
      "end_time": 870300.0,
      "text": "The Venus Project proposes using the methods of science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 870307.0,
      "end_time": 874929.0,
      "text": "applied to the social system, as a tool to elevate everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 875680.0,
      "end_time": 879156.0,
      "text": "This can be achieved by a global resource-based economy;"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 879360.0,
      "end_time": 880904.0,
      "text": "a systems approach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 881347.0,
      "end_time": 885187.0,
      "text": "where all the interacting variables are working efficiently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 885833.0,
      "end_time": 890307.0,
      "text": "as one entire process. It includes, well-..."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 890984.0,
      "end_time": 895261.0,
      "text": "new, well-designed cities that think, working symbiotically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 896683.0,
      "end_time": 898923.0,
      "text": "as a living, breathing system."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 899273.0,
      "end_time": 902683.0,
      "text": "These cities would incorporate clean sources of energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 902836.0,
      "end_time": 904732.0,
      "text": "efficient transportation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 905895.0,
      "end_time": 908486.0,
      "text": "automated production and distribution plants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 908701.0,
      "end_time": 912646.0,
      "text": "enabling-... freely making available"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 912843.0,
      "end_time": 917963.0,
      "text": "all the goods and services that a highly technological society can produce."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 918836.0,
      "end_time": 923464.0,
      "text": "Industrial plants would be turning out products that are long lasting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 924360.0,
      "end_time": 925747.0,
      "text": "and can be recycled."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 926233.0,
      "end_time": 928246.0,
      "text": "Resource surveys would be made,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 928966.0,
      "end_time": 932990.0,
      "text": "in order to find out the parameters that we have to work within."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 934467.0,
      "end_time": 938600.0,
      "text": "And before any large projects would be taken on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 938160.0,
      "end_time": 941372.0,
      "text": "we would be doing a negative and positive study."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 942830.0,
      "end_time": 943850.0,
      "text": "In other words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 943975.0,
      "end_time": 948180.0,
      "text": "we would work within the carrying capacity of Earth’s resources,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 948233.0,
      "end_time": 951925.0,
      "text": "where all the resources would become the common heritage"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 952600.0,
      "end_time": 953507.0,
      "text": "of all people."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 954344.0,
      "end_time": 957575.0,
      "text": "This, in turn, along with a new orientation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 957784.0,
      "end_time": 961163.0,
      "text": "would enable people to update their values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 962550.0,
      "end_time": 964270.0,
      "text": "and change their behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 965126.0,
      "end_time": 968300.0,
      "text": "When goods and services are made available to everyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 968572.0,
      "end_time": 970436.0,
      "text": "there is no need to steal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 971938.0,
      "end_time": 975550.0,
      "text": "when anyone can get whatever they need at the access center."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 976670.0,
      "end_time": 979889.0,
      "text": "Behaviors such as underselling your competitor"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 979993.0,
      "end_time": 983507.0,
      "text": "to knock them out of business, would become obsolete."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 984806.0,
      "end_time": 989440.0,
      "text": "What we consider a wise and shrewd business person of today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 990300.0,
      "end_time": 995330.0,
      "text": "would be looked upon as vulgar and twisted in a saner society."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 995563.0,
      "end_time": 996172.0,
      "text": "(Yeah.)"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 997261.0,
      "end_time": 1001544.0,
      "text": "People would not be looked upon as prey for a sale."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 1002500.0,
      "end_time": 1006414.0,
      "text": "People of the future would be concerned about bettering one another,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 1006600.0,
      "end_time": 1008260.0,
      "text": "rather than beating them."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 1009220.0,
      "end_time": 1012976.0,
      "text": "In medicine, for instance, people doing surgery"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 1012210.0,
      "end_time": 1016769.0,
      "text": "would not do it to get a higher salary, or acclaim, or rewards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 1017580.0,
      "end_time": 1021655.0,
      "text": "but because they get their fulfillment out of making people well."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 1023130.0,
      "end_time": 1025148.0,
      "text": "We have to build an environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 1025510.0,
      "end_time": 1028877.0,
      "text": "that generates a viewpoint that is"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 1029970.0,
      "end_time": 1033170.0,
      "text": "cooperative, rather than competitive."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 1033780.0,
      "end_time": 1039512.0,
      "text": "The more intelligent we become, the less we want to beat anyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 1040290.0,
      "end_time": 1043108.0,
      "text": "And whatever is being designed in the culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 1043930.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1048373.0000000001,
      "text": "goes right back into society, for everyone’s benefit and security."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 1048870.0,
      "end_time": 1052163.0,
      "text": "This way people are more amiable towards one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 1052700.0,
      "end_time": 1054959.0,
      "text": "But they&#39;re not more friendly towards one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 1055700.0,
      "end_time": 1059600.0,
      "text": "because we’re superimposing a moral code, or an ethical code,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 1059730.0,
      "end_time": 1061644.0,
      "text": "or teaching them empathy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 1061990.0,
      "end_time": 1065295.0,
      "text": "but because their actions genuinely"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 1065990.0,
      "end_time": 1068950.0,
      "text": "enhance the standard of living for everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 1069650.0,
      "end_time": 1072727.0,
      "text": "We call this \"functional\" morality."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 1074720.0,
      "end_time": 1076418.0,
      "text": "In a saner society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 1076820.0,
      "end_time": 1080346.0,
      "text": "people would probably feel sorry for those"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 1080840.0,
      "end_time": 1085701.0,
      "text": "who still need ostentatious waste, a bigger home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 1085880.0,
      "end_time": 1089530.0,
      "text": "or a fancier car, or more expensive jewelry."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 1090110.0,
      "end_time": 1095120.0,
      "text": "They would understand that these people are so insecure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 1095250.0,
      "end_time": 1098197.0,
      "text": "that they need to impress others in this way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 1098410.0,
      "end_time": 1101960.0,
      "text": "to acquire their own sense of self-worth."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 1103300.0,
      "end_time": 1108297.0,
      "text": "But if all the homes and all the amenities were of equal high quality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 1108600.0,
      "end_time": 1112655.0,
      "text": "no one would envy anyone over possessions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1113270.0,
      "end_time": 1116778.0,
      "text": "when anyone can get whatever anyone else has."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1119210.0,
      "end_time": 1123400.0,
      "text": "If you are envious, say of somebody who can draw better than you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1123970.0,
      "end_time": 1126818.0,
      "text": "it’s only because somebody got to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1126960.0,
      "end_time": 1128978.0,
      "text": "and said \"YOU have to be the best."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1129120.0,
      "end_time": 1130860.0,
      "text": "We would be proud of you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1131380.0,
      "end_time": 1134525.0,
      "text": "But those types of values wouldn’t be used in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1134970.0,
      "end_time": 1137739.0,
      "text": "And shame - if you had shame, it would be-..."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1138260.0,
      "end_time": 1141374.0,
      "text": "it IS because somebody convinced YOU"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1142140.0,
      "end_time": 1146928.0,
      "text": "that you are not where THEY think you ought to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1147540.0,
      "end_time": 1150279.0,
      "text": "These would be obsolete values in the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1150970.0,
      "end_time": 1154730.0,
      "text": "because the environment would enable everybody to be comfortable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1154850.0,
      "end_time": 1156388.0,
      "text": "no matter where they were."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1157620.0,
      "end_time": 1162112.0,
      "text": "In conclusion, science applies to everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1162550.0,
      "end_time": 1167357.0,
      "text": "But it’s practically non-existent when it comes to applying it"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1167830.0,
      "end_time": 1169953.0,
      "text": "to the way we organize society."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1171210.0,
      "end_time": 1174704.0,
      "text": "The Venus Project applies the methods of science"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1175000.0,
      "end_time": 1177304.0,
      "text": "to the way we operate society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1177140.0,
      "end_time": 1181182.0,
      "text": "to generate constructive and co-operative behaviors."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1181990.0,
      "end_time": 1187787.0,
      "text": "This is the most needed scientific experiment of our times."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1188300.0,
      "end_time": 1193388.0,
      "text": "And it is the most taboo to even consider, or talk about."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1194470.0,
      "end_time": 1197972.0,
      "text": "What we have now is a failed experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1198290.0,
      "end_time": 1202794.0,
      "text": "It does not meet the needs and it does not enrich the lives of everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1203460.0,
      "end_time": 1206922.0,
      "text": "What we ultimately do will depend"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1206290.0,
      "end_time": 1209271.0,
      "text": "on if we have a future or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1209860.0,
      "end_time": 1212242.0,
      "text": "So we invite you to join us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1212250.0,
      "end_time": 1216742.0,
      "text": "in what could be the most exciting and rewarding social experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1216840.0,
      "end_time": 1219270.0,
      "text": "that we could possibly take on."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1219990.0,
      "end_time": 1220704.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 1221290.0,
      "end_time": 1224391.0,
      "text": "[Applause]"
    }
  ]
}